{"id": "art-25143", "label": "Art. 25143", "title": "Art. 25143", "slug": "art-25143", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_242722037\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1506\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_242722037\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>43</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_272734908\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1505\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_272734908\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Administratorii\nsau, dup&#259; caz, membrii directoratului întocmesc un proiect de transformare\ntransfrontalier&#259; care trebuie s&#259; cuprind&#259; cel <span\nclass=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_391996584\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1504\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_391996584\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)forma juridic&#259; de societate, firma <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul social ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nce face obiectul transform&#259;rii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1091409528\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1503\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1091409528\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)forma juridic&#259; de societate, firma/denumirea <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul social ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ntransformate în statul de <span class=SpellE>destina&#355;ie</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1147862429\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1502\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1147862429\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)calendarul orientativ propus pentru transformarea\ntransfrontalier&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_526848201\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1501\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_526848201\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)drepturile acordate de societatea transformat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale sau alte titluri de valoare\nreprezentând capitalul social care confer&#259; drepturi speciale în societatea\ncare se transform&#259; sau m&#259;surile propuse în <span class=SpellE>privin&#355;a</span>\nacestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2111882610\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1500\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2111882610\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)orice <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> acordate\ncreditorilor, precum <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;iile</span> reale <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau personale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_258285843\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1499\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_258285843\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)orice avantaje speciale acordate administratorilor ori\ndirectorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, membrilor consiliului de supraveghere sau\ndirectoratului;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_356878695\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1498\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_356878695\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privitoare la\nprimirea, dac&#259; este cazul, a unor ajutoare de stat sau a altor forme de\nsprijin din partea statului în ultimii 5 ani;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_430319725\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1497\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_430319725\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)<span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ul</span> <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale sau altor titluri de\nvaloare reprezentând capitalul social ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>,\npentru <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> în care <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>î&#351;i</span> exercit&#259; dreptul de retragere din\nsocietate, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> adresa de e-mail la care <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> pot transmite <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span>\nde retragere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_11954456\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1496\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_11954456\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)<span class=SpellE>implica&#355;iile</span>\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere asupra <span class=SpellE>for&#355;ei</span>\nde munc&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_33892384\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1495\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_33892384\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> cu privire la\nprocedurile de stabilire a particip&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a altor <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nde implicare a acestora în societatea transformat&#259;, dac&#259; este cazul.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1621765204\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1494\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1621765204\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Proiectul de transformare transfrontalier&#259; are, în\nanex&#259;, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iile</span> financiare întocmite în\nvederea transform&#259;rii, aprobate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> auditate\npotrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, ce nu pot fi mai\nvechi de 6 luni <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de data proiectului de\ntransformare, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> actul constitutiv al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> transformate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1297758191\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1493\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1297758191\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cu cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;ase</span> s&#259;pt&#259;mâni înainte de data întrunirii\nadun&#259;rii generale convocate s&#259; aprobe transformarea\ntransfrontalier&#259; a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nproiectul de transformare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> anexele acestuia se\npun la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>,\ncel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> în format electronic, prin <span\nclass=SpellE>afi&#351;are</span> pe pagina de internet a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 251<sup>47</sup>\nalin. (3), sau prin transmitere pe cale electronic&#259;, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ii</span>\nprimind <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> o notificare în conformitate cu art.\n251<sup>47</sup> alin. (1).</span></p>"}